[00:50] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'eventually you get something that kind of looks like what you\'re looking for. Now, if you\'re not careful with the prompts, that can mean that you\'re sitting on your computer for hours at a time. And again, just really interacting and kind of chatting with an agent trying to get some desired output. Now,'

[01:03] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Blitzy takes a completely opposite approach where rather than doing this kind of iterative back and forth approach, what you do is you spend a lot more time up front generating a really detailed or kind of long spec or prompt.'

[01:15] [scene:talk]
